flowchart TB
    UI[Client] --> POST["Producer<br/>POST /chatbot/messages"]
    POST -->|Kafka chatbot-requests| PROC[ProcessChatHandler]
    POST -->|Redis subscribe| SSE[SSE → Client]

    PROC --> RESP["OpenAI Responses<br/>previous_response_id 체이닝"]
    RESP -->|function_call| TOOLS["Tools<br/>inventory · search_recipes<br/>categories · finalize"]
    TOOLS -->|function_call_output| RESP
    TOOLS --> SEARCH["search_recipes<br/>해상 → expand → ANN → 재랭킹"]

    RESP -->|chunk · tool_call · done| REDIS[(Redis stream)]
    REDIS --> SSE
    SSE --> UI

    RESP --> POST_PROC["크레딧 차감 · ChatbotLog<br/>Conversation 메타"]

    style POST fill:#e0234e,color:#fff
    style PROC fill:#e0234e,color:#fff
    style RESP fill:#10a37f,color:#fff
    style REDIS fill:#dc382d,color:#fff
